Class BasicMigrationNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tsgrp.migration.node.BasicMigrationNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MigrationNode

    public class BasicMigrationNode
extends java.lang.Object
implements MigrationNode
    Complete implementation of MigrationNode which can, while complete, be subclassed by the Source as it deems fit.
